<li>Cherish the memories; they are a precious gift.</li>
<li>May your memories of [deceased's name] bring you comfort and peace.</li>
<li>May the beautiful memories of [deceased's name] forever remain in your heart.</li>
<li>Hold onto the love you shared and find solace in those treasured moments.</li>
<li>Let your memories bring smiles to your face, even amidst your sadness.</li>
<li>May your peace grow stronger with each passing day.</li>
<li>May the love you shared with [deceased's name] be a source of comfort.</li>
<li>Embrace the peaceful memories of your loved one.</li>
<li>Remember the joy and laughter you shared.  Those memories will forever remain.</li>
<li>May you find moments of peace amongst your sorrow.</li>
<li>Find comfort in knowing [deceased's name] lived a beautiful life.</li>
<li>May your heart find solace in the love that surrounds you.</li>
